name: Robot Metropolis Carnival Series 6/10
description: The Robot Metropolis Carnival. The focused mouse knew that without entertainment, the visitors would soon get bored by the novelty of the crazed, dazed, and even the focused population. Out of dire necessity the bright ghost was crafted. Without brain, it is mostly an emanation of waves coming from all within the carnival except for the dazed child, who is without any waves at all.
